News.Title: Identical Brains Studios: Shares Debut with 76% Premium on NSE SME
News.Summary: Identical Brains Studios shares listed at ₹95, a 75.9% premium over the issue price of ₹54 on the NSE SME platform. The IPO, worth ₹19.95 crore, was oversubscribed 544.28 times. Funds raised will be used for studio renovation, new office establishment, and equipment purchases.
